{"tid":343632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每日一片：直擊無人機大圍90米高空急墜","createTime":"2017-08-01T15:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T17:34:47.000Z","uid":16697,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4897018d7374eef8279a967fc5a71bc0e2c9b5e9","tid":343632,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:13:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170801/bkn-20170801191116670-0801_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170801%2Fbkn-20170801191116670-0801_00822_001.html&d=%2F1R3kjJOvyM4pFnsqpqDSjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ae00f565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170801/bkn-20170801191116670-0801_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170801/photo/bkn-20170801191116670-0801_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170801224111\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170801191116670-0801_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170801224111&h=e583f999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無人機風氣盛行，正當民航處擬修例加強規管無人機之際，近日網上就流傳一條無人機失事的意外短片，第一身直擊無人機在高樓大廈林立的大圍住宅區墜機一刻，令人反思無人機的安全問題。<br />\n<br />\n該片段疑用穿越式遙控無人機在大圍附近拍攝，上載片段的網民稱，當時在約90米高空拍攝，正俯瞰大圍一帶。起初無人機在高空飛行時尚算穩定，但其後未知是否受到高樓的天線干擾，開始旋轉及左搖右擺，最後航拍機失控。短短數秒，無人機由高空急墜到地上，跌落一個私人屋苑停車場旁的樹林，期間不斷發出墜機的警報聲，還幸未有造成任何人受傷或其他財物損壞。<br />\n<br />\n有網民表示幸好沒砸到任何人，否則到時「出人命」，有人懷疑因機體無電或離開控制範圍導致"},{"pid":"4c68b61bab4a4637e70432f9c6c816813511a1fa","tid":343632,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87820ea7bb95be2a4a48f76da1ade32a0d7097fa","tid":343632,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f125b3912b62f831a45289ba4a350b8fb5080e82","tid":343632,"uid":32114,"like":1,